OL,3,CFirms fined after worker crushed by
OL,4,Cskips at Pirelli factory site
OL,6,FOne of Carlisle's biggest employers
OL,7,Fhas been fined #280,000 after a worker
OL,8,Fsuffered multiple back fractures when
OL,9,Fhe was hit by two falling skips.
OL,11,FPirelli and two other companies have
OL,12,Fbeen fined for health and safety
OL,13,Ffailings after a man sustained "long-
OL,14,Flasting, life-altering injuries" at
OL,15,FCarlisle's Pirelli tyre factory.
OL,17,FIRTR and DCS Multiserve, the
OL,18,Fcontractors responsible for disposing
OL,19,Fof waste tyres and were also fined for
OL,20,Ffailings.
