OL,6,FPirelli was handed the maximum fine of
OL,7,F#280,000, while IRTR was ordered to
OL,8,Fpay #9,000 and DCS was fined #2,600.
OL,10,FService engineer Ivan Weightman, who
OL,11,Fwas not employed by any of the three
OL,12,Fcompanies, was visiting the city's
OL,13,FDalston Road complex on 14 November
OL,14,F2019, to inspect a forklift truck.
OL,16,FThe court heard that the two skips
OL,17,Fwhich were precariously balanced on
OL,18,Fwaste tyres to compress them, when
OL,19,Fthey fell and struck his back and leg.
