OL,6,FMr Weightman sustained a number of
OL,7,Finjuries including multiple spinal
OL,8,Ffractures, a broken femur and nerve
OL,9,Fcompression.
OL,11,FIn a statement, he described being in
OL,12,Fhospital for five days after the
OL,13,Fincident, where he underwent surgery.
OL,15,FHe also described the long lasting
OL,16,Feffects the incident had had on his
OL,17,Fphysical and mental heath, saying he
OL,18,Fhad been anti-depressant medication
OL,19,Ffor at least four years.
