OL,6,FCarlisle Crown Court heard how the
OL,7,F"improvised, unsafe" practice of using
OL,8,Fa forklift to place a loaded
OL,9,Findustiral skip on top of waste tyres
OL,10,Fto compress them, was being used
OL,11,Finstead of the specialist machine.
OL,13,FProsecutor Mark Monaghan said: "It was
OL,14,Fan improvised, unsafe practice of work
OL,15,Fthat was allowed to persist over a
OL,16,Flong period of time,"
OL,18,FHe told the court that Pirelli "knew
OL,19,Fit was happening", adding that "it was
OL,20,Fan inherently unsafe process", which
OL,21,F"should have been stopped".
