OL,6,F"Two skips had been loaded on to a
OL,7,Ftyre stack ready for that squashing
OL,8,Fprocess prior to Mr Weightman's visit
OL,9,Fin November, 2019.
OL,11,F"Mr Weightman, totally unaware of the
OL,12,Fprecarious procedure, reversed the
OL,13,Fforklift truck away from the stack
OL,14,Fahead of a mandatory inspection, and
OL,15,Fwalked around it."
OL,17,F"As he did so, the skips fell," said
OL,18,FMr Monaghan.
