OL,6,FRepresentatives of each firm submitted
OL,7,Fa formal basis for admissions of guilt.
OL,9,FImprovements had been made by all
OL,10,Fthree firms to ensure all strict rules
OL,11,Fwere followed.
OL,13,FBarrister Richard Matthews KC, for
OL,14,FPirelli, said: "The company regrets
OL,15,Fthis enormously."
OL,17,FHe added: "Everybody at Pirelli
OL,18,Frecognises and regrets these human
OL,19,Fcosts.
