OL,6,F"Pirelli does take health and safety
OL,7,Fseriously and has systems in place to
OL,8,Fkeep its over 1,000 employees 150-200
OL,9,Fcontractors safe.
OL,11,F"It's intention is to learn everything
OL,12,Fpossible from this to ensure nothing
OL,13,Fsimilar happens again."
OL,15,FCounsel representing DCS and IRTR also
OL,16,Fexpressed regret and remorse.
OL,18,FIn conclusion the judge said: "It is
OL,19,Fobvious that the practice that had
OL,20,Fbeen allowed to perpetuate for so long
OL,21,Fwas potentially a lethal practice."
